Interface Hkt<M extends Witness,a>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - The witness type.
    a - A type parameter.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Witness
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Hkt2<M,a,b>, Hkt3<M,a,b,c>, Hkt4<M,a,b,c,d>, Hkt5<M,a,b,c,d,e>, Hkt6<M,a,b,c,d,e,f>, Hkt7<M,a,b,c,d,e,f,g>, Hkt8<M,a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Either, Either.Left, Either.LeftProjection, Either.Right, Either.RightProjection, FList, FList.Cons, FList.Nil, Identity, Maybe, Maybe.Just, Maybe.None, MaybeT, ReaderT, ReaderT.Reader, Stack, Try, Try.TryT, WriterT, WriterT.Writer
